title: The Rush Limbaugh Radio Show SEP-04-2013 WED Edited
description:
This is the Rush Limbaugh Radio Show kindly uploaded by CAPTAIN7SS with several minutes of commercials edited out. There is one block about 15 minutes in and another block about 15 minutes from the end of each hour. Another block at about the middle of each hour is already removed. 

Edits are not terribly precise, but I think are useful. Your comments welcome.
